                            "termSource": null,
                            "termAccession": ""
                        },
                        "description": "<p>After the samples were slowly thawed at 4 \u00b0C, an appropriate amount of samples were added to pre-chilled methanol:acetonitrile aqueous solution (2:2:1, v/v). Vortex mix, low temperature ultrasonic 30 min, -20 \u00b0C stand for 10 min, 14000 x g, 4 \u00b0C centrifugation for 20 min, vacuum drying, then for mass spectrometry analysis added 100 \u03bcL acetonitrile aqueous solution (acetonitrile:water, 1:1, v/v) reconstitution, vortex, 14000 x g 4 \u00b0C centrifugation for 15 min and injection.</p>",
